{
  "stem": "13524.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Wooden 10 tables through the length of our standing there. 10 people to each table were selected from that group of the 10,000, surrounded with SS with guns.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But beforehand, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was few people to be hanged-- four.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Two people I knew very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One was engineer Krautfeer, and the other boy's name was Helbenshtock, young boy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were told, you know, told by somebody that they were running away from the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So that's why they were caught and they're going to be hanged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was to scare us never to try to run away, because whoever did-- we did know that people did try to run away-- and they were shot.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And on this occasion, they said that every-- out of every 100 persons, one is going to be shot every-- so [INAUDIBLE] sure enough, the people-- one of them, that engineer Krautfeer, already committed suicide beforehand.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He cut his wrists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Dead as he was, he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The other two people were standing there waiting to be hanged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There was another boy, Helbenshtock, to be hanged, and he was being hanged by somebody with-- who was trying desperately to save his life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he fell once, twice, three times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Because they thought that if he will fall, his life will be spared, according to the Geneva convention.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "His life was not only not spared.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But Goeth pulled out his gun, and he said to the man who was hanging him, if you won't hang him, you will be hanged and I shoot you here.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, it was Amon Goeth in every performance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taking the main part in everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The boy was hanged-- young boy, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
